title: ‘Fifty Shades Darker’ Actress Made Quite A Statement In This Dress On The Red Carpet
text:
TOP 5461825 
Dakota Johnson turned quite a few heads when she showed up on the red carpet Thursday at the premiere of her film “Fifty Shades Darker” showing a lot of skin. 
The 27-year-old actress and star of the highly anticipated sequel to “Fifty Shades of Grey” appeared at the Ace Hotel in Los Angeles, California in a pale pink dress without a bra. (VIDEO: ‘Fifty Shades Of Grey’ Star Called Filming In Nice After Terror Attack ‘Sobering’) (photo by: Xavier Collin/IPA/Splash News) 
In the shot, Johnson wore a sleeveless gown with a plunging neckline that showed off a lot of cleavage. (RELATED: ‘Fifty Shades Darker’ Trailer Beats 24-Hour Record Set By ‘The Force Awakens’ [VIDEO]) (photo by: Russ Einhorn / Splash News) (photo by: Jen Lowery / Splash News) (photo by: Xavier Collin/IPA/Splash News) 
The erotic romance movie marks the return of Johnson as Anastasia Steele and Jamie Dornan as Christian Grey. “Fifty Shades Darker” hits theaters on Valentine’s Day. (Photo by Xavier Collin/Image Press Agency/Splash News) (Photo by Xavier Collin/Image Press Agency/Splash News)
